DESCRIPTION:All first semester Media School majors are invited to join our
  academic advisors and program faculty directors for key advising reminde
 rs and beginning connections to others in your Media major. Dean Tolchins
 ky will welcome you to The Media School and kickoff your academic journey
  at your new home. Students will then breakout into their major specific 
 sessions to understand key requirements and student involvement opportuni
 ties to position them for success and to better define where to start.\n\
 nHosted by: The Media School Undergraduate Program\n\nAdditional Informat
 ion can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12440011
